%% Diagram: Core Execution Model Showing The Flow Between Task Queue Event Loop And Call Sta
%% Type: flowchart
graph LR
    subgraph "Execution Model"
        A[Task Queue] --> B[Event Loop]
        B --> C[Call Stack]
        C --> D[Function Execution]
        D --> E[Return/Complete]
        E --> F[Stack Empty?]
        F -->|Yes| G[Next Task]
        F -->|No| D
        G --> A
    end
